name: Oinkologne
flavorText: Oinkologne is proud of its fine, glossy skin. It emits a concentrated scent from the tip of its tail.

previous.name: Lechonk
previous.flavorText: It searches for food all day. It possesses a keen sense of smell but doesn’t use it for anything other than foraging.

next.name: Tarountula
next.flavorText: The ball of threads wrapped around its body is elastic enough to deflect the scythes of Scyther, this Pokémon’s natural enemy.
